      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint chipping on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few faint stains, though all essential electronics and the air conditioning remain functional. Mechanically, it runs consistently, but it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating shape.",
